00:25:33.950 --> 00:25:39.350
of this project, Beyond Curie,
and how can girls and women

00:25:39.350 --> 00:25:41.982
access it, and connect
to these messages

00:25:41.982 --> 00:25:43.190
that you're trying to convey?

00:25:43.190 --> 00:25:44.731
AMANDA PHINGBODHIPAKKIYA:
Absolutely.

00:25:44.731 --> 00:25:47.120
So it lives online
at beyondcurie.com.

00:25:47.120 --> 00:25:49.490
We do a lot of exhibits
around the country

00:25:49.490 --> 00:25:52.700
and around the world that
shows these portraits,

00:25:52.700 --> 00:25:56.300
gives a small little description
of what these scientists

00:25:56.300 --> 00:25:59.330
and technologists have
contributed to the world,

00:25:59.330 --> 00:26:03.690
and also there's an AR app in
the Apple and Android store.

00:26:07.374 --> 00:26:08.207
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:26:08.207 --> 00:26:09.061
AMANDA PHINGBODHIPAKKIYA: Sure.

00:26:09.061 --> 00:26:10.900
Oh, there's also a
Kickstarter that we're

00:26:10.900 --> 00:26:14.080
