that's holiday cards,

00:26:14.080 --> 00:26:16.900
in case you're
interested in sharing

00:26:16.900 --> 00:26:18.700
these women for the holidays.

00:26:21.836 --> 00:26:23.960
AUDIENCE: Have you considered
working with schools,

00:26:23.960 --> 00:26:26.960
or are you working with
schools around the country,

00:26:26.960 --> 00:26:34.324
to encourage girls be made aware
of, and girls and boys, really?

00:26:34.324 --> 00:26:36.240
AMANDA PHINGBODHIPAKKIYA:
That's a great idea.

00:26:36.240 --> 00:26:39.120
We are working with
several schools.

00:26:39.120 --> 00:26:42.780
It's kind of come
about organically.

00:26:42.780 --> 00:26:45.890
We field a lot of
inbound from schools,

00:26:45.890 --> 00:26:49.100
and we donate a lot of
